name: [Finger Detection] onFingerDetected - onFingerRemoved - onFingerDetectionTimeExpired
description:
The *onFingerDetected* will Fire when a finger is detected.

The *onFingerRemoved* will Fire when a finger is removed.

The *onFingerDetectionTimeExpired* will Fire when the finger detection time is expired (must be set by fingerDetectionExpiryTime)
